snippet.title: Sayaka’s Addiction - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
There are many ways to go about the game and progress the story. Money can be earned in many different ways and through a variety of minigames. Want to work earnestly at a part-time job? Go for it! Want to work as a waitress? That’s also an option!

Sayaka’s Addiction on Kagura Games Store: https://www.kaguragames.com/product/sayakas-addiction/

Sayaka’s Addiction on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3421070/Sayakas_Addiction/
